    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD stands as a superlative specimen of rotary performance, featuring the iconic 13B-REW power plant with its sequential twin-turbocharger configuration delivering a seamless power band. The chassis maintains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension that offers unparalleled turn-in precision. Every mechanical component, from the Torsen limited-slip differential to the crisp five-speed manual gearbox, operates with the tactile feedback expected of a showroom-quality vehicle. The exterior retains its original deep-luster finish, while the cockpit is a time capsule of driver-centric ergonomics, free of wear or UV degradation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade FD that has been meticulously maintained to preserve its high-revving soul and legendary handling dynamics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
