    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a stunning deep-gloss paint that has been protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free from stone chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks. This car has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface operates with factory-spec tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance regimen with a fully organized binder of service records included. The engine bay is detailed to a show-standard, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash, wrapped in a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a turn-key example in absolute peak condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
